## 2. Detailed Code Changes

### 2.1 Setlist State and Providers
**File**: `lib/features/setlist/presentation/setlist_providers.dart`
- Add a state provider for the stack toggle:
  ```dart
  final appendAtEndOfListProvider = StateProvider<bool>((ref) => false);
  ```
- Add a slide-to-setlist mapping provider to match slide index to setlist item index:
  ```dart
  final slideToSetlistItemIndexProvider = Provider<List<int>>((ref) {
    final setlist = ref.watch(setlistProvider);
    if (setlist.isEmpty) return [];
    final List<int> mapping = [];
    for (int itemIdx = 0; itemIdx < setlist.length; itemIdx++) {
      final item = setlist[itemIdx];
      if (item is SongSetlistItem) {
        final isSong = item.song.author != 'Bible';
        final count = SlideUtils.parseLyrics(item.song.lyrics, item.song.title, isSong: isSong, isFavorite: item.isFavorite).length;
        for (int i = 0; i < count; i++) mapping.add(itemIdx);
      } else if (item is ImageSetlistItem) {
        mapping.add(itemIdx); // Image slide
        mapping.add(itemIdx); // Trailing blank slide
      }
    }
    return mapping;
  });
  ```
- Add a provider to get the currently displaying setlist item index:
  ```dart
  final currentDisplayItemIndexProvider = Provider<int?>((ref) {
    final slides = ref.watch(currentSlidesProvider);
    if (slides.isEmpty) return null;
    final activeIndex = ref.watch(activeSlideIndexProvider);
    final mapping = ref.watch(slideToSetlistItemIndexProvider);
    if (activeIndex < 0 || activeIndex >= mapping.length) return null;
    return mapping[activeIndex];
  });
  ```
- Add a helper to compute slide indices:
  ```dart
  int getSlideCountForItems(List<SetlistItem> items, int upToIndex) {
    int count = 0;
    for (int i = 0; i <= upToIndex; i++) {
      if (i >= items.length) break;
      final item = items[i];
      if (item is SongSetlistItem) {
        final isSong = item.song.author != 'Bible';
        count += SlideUtils.parseLyrics(item.song.lyrics, item.song.title, isSong: isSong, isFavorite: item.isFavorite).length;
      } else if (item is ImageSetlistItem) {
        count += 2;
      }
    }
    return count;
  }
  ```

### 2.2 Scroll Centering & Highlights on Slide List
**File**: `lib/features/dashboard/presentation/widgets/preview_pane.dart`
- Modify the `activeSlideIndexProvider` listener to center scroll alignment:
  ```dart
  ref.listen(activeSlideIndexProvider, (previous, next) {
    if (scrollController.hasClients) {
      const itemHeight = 28.0;
      final viewportHeight = scrollController.position.viewportDimension;
      final maxScroll = scrollController.position.maxScrollExtent;
      final centerOffset = (next * itemHeight) - (viewportHeight / 2) + (itemHeight / 2);
      scrollController.animateTo(
        centerOffset.clamp(0.0, maxScroll),
        duration: const Duration(milliseconds: 200),
        curve: Curves.easeInOut,
      );
    }
  });
  ```
- Pass purple highlight status to `SlideItemWidget`:
  ```dart
  final slideToItemMapping = ref.watch(slideToSetlistItemIndexProvider);
  final slideItemIndex = index < slideToItemMapping.length ? slideToItemMapping[index] : null;
  final selectedItems = ref.watch(setlistSelectionProvider);
  final isItemCurrentlySelected = slideItemIndex != null && selectedItems.contains(slideItemIndex);
  
  final activeIndex = ref.watch(activeSlideIndexProvider);
  final currentDisplayItemIndex = activeIndex < slideToItemMapping.length ? slideToItemMapping[activeIndex] : null;
  
  final isPurpleHighlighted = isItemCurrentlySelected && slideItemIndex != currentDisplayItemIndex;
  ```

